01:22:52,668 --> 01:22:54,401
Unbelievable!

931
01:22:54,403 --> 01:22:56,437
Oh, Harris is down!

932
01:22:56,439 --> 01:22:57,438
Mike Harris is down.

933
01:22:57,440 --> 01:22:59,039
